<HL>
   West German Wholesale Prices
</HL>
<DATE>
07/12/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A8
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP
</CO>
<LP>
   FRANKFURT, West Germany -- Wholesale prices in West
Germany in June eased 0.3% from May and were off 0.2% from
June 1989, the Federal Statistics Office said.
   The declines continued a trend toward modest inflationary
tendencies this year. In May, wholesale prices rose 0.3% from
April and were up 0.2% from May 1989.
</LP>
